maintext:
CLEVELAND (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday evening’s drawing of the Ohio Lottery’s “Classic Lotto” game were:
11-14-27-32-42-47, Kicker: 1-2-1-2-3-5
(eleven, fourteen, twenty-seven, thirty-two, forty-two, forty-seven; Kicker: one, two, one, two, three, five)
Estimated jackpot: $11.7 million
